    {
      "id": "PopularPost88835",
      "post_content": "Why is everyone rating this so low...  \nThis is one of the best land destruction spells due to its speed.  \nIt's ideal in a ![Red or Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=RG&type=symbol) LD deck (like mine) which simultaneously gains and destroys land. With this you'll always keep your opponent down; and with your ramping spells, you'll never fall behind.   \n  \nAs early as turn 4 you can destroy two lands ([Raze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raze) + [Stone Rain](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stone Rain)) which will put you at an easy advantage despite being down one land (easily fixed).  \n  \nAs with every LD deck, you want to make sure you go first so you'll always have the edge.",
      "posted_by": "Blackworm_Bloodworm",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost88835\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Why is everyone rating this so low...<br/>This is one of the best land destruction spells due to its speed.<br/>It's ideal in a <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red or Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=RG&amp;type=symbol\"/> LD deck (like mine) which simultaneously gains and destroys land. With this you'll always keep your opponent down; and with your ramping spells, you'll never fall behind. <br/><br/>As early as turn 4 you can destroy two lands (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Raze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raze\">Raze</a> + <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stone Rain\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stone Rain\">Stone Rain</a>) which will put you at an easy advantage despite being down one land (easily fixed).<br/><br/>As with every LD deck, you want to make sure you go first so you'll always have the edge.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '88835'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy29658\">Blackworm_Bloodworm</span>\r\n                                (7/18/2010 2:24:46 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n           